name: AcrobatCompatibility
shortdesc: The exported PDF document's Acrobat compatibility.

property.name: ACROBAT_4
property.shortdesc: Makes the file compatible with Acrobat 4.0 and later.

property.name: ACROBAT_5
property.shortdesc: Makes the file compatible with Acrobat 5.0 and later.

property.name: ACROBAT_6
property.shortdesc: Makes the file compatible with Acrobat 6.0 and later.

property.name: ACROBAT_7
property.shortdesc: Makes the file compatible with Acrobat 7.0 or higher.
